Class Employee

java.lang.Object
dryclean.cyprusDryCleanEntities.User
dryclean.cyprusDryCleanEntities.Employee
public class Employee extends User
Represents an employee in the system. Employees have unique IDs, work-related details, and health inspection records. Extends the User class.
Version:
23.0
Author:
Ferhat Kasim Koc
